                     <interp inst="t18121202-63-defend715" type="age" value="32"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18121202-63-off365" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18121202-63-off365" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18121202-63-off365" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18121202-63-cd366" type="crimeDate">23d of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18121202-63-off365 t18121202-63-cd366"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18121202-63-off367 t18121202-63-cd366"></join>, a deck-stopper, value 4 s. one strap for a cross-jack yard, value 3 s. a main truss, value 1 s. a foot truss and rope for a top-sail yard, value 4 s. a pair of top-sail sheets, value 20 s. main stays, and main spring sail and yard, value 10 s. and two joints of old rope, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18121202-63-victim717" type="victimName">John Carr<interp inst="t18121202-63-victim717" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , 
               
                  <persName id="t18121202-63-victim719" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Davis
                  <interp inst="t18121202-63-victim719" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
